Electromagnetic.

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:05.000
I will just abbreviate it EM.
Next stronger force?

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:06.000
Weak force.
And the next?

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:08.000
Strong.
Weak and strong are

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:12.000
